  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110162800623\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110162800623\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'3028108_10';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">이수한의원 원장님의 공로상 &amp; 축하패</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130313_186/isuhani_1363162535153nJwt2_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2%B0%F8%B7%CE%C6%D020130309_100209.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"337\" height=\"252\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 337px; rheight: 252px\" id=\"20130313_186/isuhani_1363162535153nJwt2_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2%B0%F8%B7%CE%C6%D020130309_100209.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A636EFEF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130313_186/isuhani_1363162535153nJwt2_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2%B0%F8%B7%CE%C6%D020130309_100209.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">바뿌신 와중에도 연구에 몰두하셨던 원장님</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">대학원 졸업하시면서 공로상과 후배님들한테서 축하패까지</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">받으신 원장님</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">축하하는 마음에서 기록을 남겨봅니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">[사당동 이수한의원]</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</